lass="t m0 x12 h4f y31a ff13 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws3">___________________________<span class="_ _8"></span>__<span class="_ _8"></span>_<span class="_ _8"></span>__<span class="_ _8"></span>________________________</div><div class="t m0 x54 h5 y31b ff14 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 wsa1">Without a doubt, the Bible reveals a God who is greatly involved </div><div class="t m0 x12 h5 y31c ff14 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws90">with humanity. The whole great-controversy scenario is, really, about </div><div class="t m0 x12 h5 y31d ff14 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 wsca">how the Lord is working to save humanity from the clutches of sin </div><div class="t m0 x12 h5 y31e ff14 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws24">and Satan. From the first act of the earth’s creation <span class="ff13">(Gen. 1:1)</span> to the </div><div class="t m0 x12 h5 y31f ff14 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws3">cross <span class="_ _3b"> </span><span class="ff13 ws99">(John 19:18)<span class="ff14"> to the recreation of the earth </span>(2 Pet. 3:12, 13)</span>, </div><div class="t m0 x12 h5 y320 ff14 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 wsfa">the Bible shows us unequivocally the Lord’s intimate activity with </div><div class="t m0 x12 h5 y321 ff14 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws3">humanity.</div><div class="t m0 x4e h50 y322 ff15 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws80">In what ways have you, personally, experienced the activity of </div><div class="t m0 x4e h50 y323 ff15 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws57">God? In what ways have you seen Him work in your life and in </div><div class="t m0 x4e h50 y324 ff15 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws36">the lives of others? In what ways can you learn to draw comfort </div><div class="t m0 x4e h50 y325 ff15 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws6">from knowing God’s closeness and intimacy with us?</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
